reviewText: Loved it as a Child, Love it as an Adult. Perfect Pack, Works well.

If you have a Postman Pat fan this is a great DVD set. We ended up purchasing it after netflix took the series off of their instant play list. We had to also purchase a region free DVD player, but it was worth it for our kids to watch a lot of the different shows they have fallen in love with.
Good DVD set for young children who like Postman Pat.  One gets what one orders - no disappointment possible as DVDs are just that - DVDs!.

Brilliantly cheap, wonderful series, my kids love these!
Best of all, my dvd player is region free so we can watch it here in the US!
If you don't have region free DVD player, this is not for you!
I got this for my children, ages 7 and 10, for Christmas.  I think I like it more than they do.
It is in Pal system and cannot be played in United States.  I made a mistake, be careful before you purchase it.  I had seen the shows on HBO and I enjoyed it very much.  I am very disappointed.
